Class TSModel

java.lang.Object
  it.unibz.tsmodel.model.TSModel

public class TSModel
extends java.lang.Object

Author:
mreinstadler This class represents a Model used for the forecasting process. The model includes one ParkingPlace, a WekaForecaster, an object of Instances, a ModelEvaluation and finally an EvaluationStrategy used to evaluate the model
